# Unclick

**Team Members:** Armand Packham-McGuiness

**How would you pitch your game in one line?**
Think cookie clicker, but instead of making cookies, you're destrouing the universe one atom at a time

**What is the key mechanic(s) that make it fun?**
The main mechanic will be you clicking, creating automations, and expanding your powers, slowly getting faster and faster!
